    "Title": "Cull Irradiated Kopions",
    "TitleKey": "Highpoint_KillAnimals_storm_H_title_001",
    "Description": "As a consequence of the ongoing radiation storm on Pyro I, some of the invasive kopions have become irradiated. This poses a threat to the health of the indigenous wildlife and to those who live and work in <EM4>~mission(Location)</EM4>. \n\nWe are seeking out a skilled contractor who can cull any irradiated kopions in and around <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. Do not accept this contract unless you have the proper weapons and equipment that can reliably function in a radioactive environment. \n\nYour compensation will be adjusted to match the risks associated with this contract.\n\nBest,\n\nWanda Werkheiser\nContract Manager\nHighpoint Wilderness Specialists",
    "DescriptionKey": "Highpoint_KillAnimals_storm_H_desc_001",
